            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">Hi all--</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">First, I would like to wish all I-PR
            subscribers a pleasant and safe holiday season.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">I have a request for information, if
            you are able to share success stories. I am about to promote my
            book, entitled Search Engine Visibility, and I know that generating
            local interest is a good PR strategy. Do any of you have some great
            success stories you can share? Any suggestions, not necessarily in
            the same field, will be greatly appreciated.</font></p>
            <p><font face="Arial" size="2">I hired a PR person who specializes
            in the Chicago area. I'm just wondering if there are other Metro
            areas that might help.</font></p>
